#### 4. Atmospheric Mass-Balance Systems

Closed-loop counters leaks (~0.1â€“1% daily) and crew consumption.

Mass-flow: 

\[ \frac{dm_{\text{O}_2}}{dt} = r_{\text{ISRU}} - r_{\text{crew}} - r_{\text{leak}} \]

PSA energy ~1.2 kWh/kg Nâ‚‚/Ar (2025 benchmarks); trade-offs include dust filtration but enable surge recovery.

